Title : Edirkottai
Text : {{Use dmy dates|date=September 2018}}
{{Use Indian English|date=September 2018}}
{{Unreferenced|date=April 2014}}

'''Edirkottai''' is a small village in [[Sivakasi taluk]] of [[Tamil Nadu]], [[India]]. It is located 15&nbsp;km from [[Sivakasi]] and 18&nbsp;km from [[Sattur]].

